title: Boise Fry Company
typeOfFood: Lacto, American, Fast food, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Fries and burgers joint with multiple outlets. Has a vegan patty - be sure to specify. Five different fries to choose from with different cuts, different sauces that are labeled if they are vegan or not as well as different seasoning salts. Validates parking at the Civic shops retail parking garage.
